'''Archon''' (ib [[Greek language|Greek]] '''A<U+03C1><U+03C7><U+03C9><U+03BD>'''; lived [[4th century BC]]) was a [[History of Pella|Pella]]ean appointed [[satrap]] of [[Babylonia]] after the death of [[Alexander the Great]], [[323 BC]].{{rf|1|just_13.4_diod_18.3}}, is probably the same as the son of Cleinias mentioned in the [[History of India|Indian]] expedition of Alexander.{{rf|2|arr_18}}

